or those with higher optical depth to\nLyC, as expected from the photoionization models. Further investigation of a\nlarger sample of CIII]-emitters is necessary to calibrate the dependence of\nCIII] emission on the escape of LyC radiation, and to enable application of the\nCIII] diagnostics to galaxies in the reionization epoch.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 May 2020 19:52:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Jun 2020 13:58:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-01"}
