 clinicians in screening\npatients for COVID-19, thus facilitating immediate triaging and treatment for\nbetter outcomes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 May 2020 07:03:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-13"}
