tain assignments of base gate costs\nby developing an analytic model to estimate the proportion of sets of\n$Z$-rotation gates from higher orders of the Clifford hierarchy that are found\nwithin sequences approximating random target gates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 May 2020 07:21:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 May 2020 02:41:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2021 05:59:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-17"}
