eon-target nuclear potentials. The nuclear breakup component, the CNI\neffect, and the multistep breakup processes are all found to be non-negligible;\nhence, the assumptions adopted in the VPT for the accurate description of\nbreakup cross sections are not valid.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 May 2020 08:23:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 29 Apr 2021 16:59:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-11"}
