.112008","report-no":null,"categories":"hep-ex hep-ph","license":"http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/","abstract":"  The processes $e^+e^-\\to D_s^+ D_{s1}(2460)^- +c.c.$ and $e^+e^-\\to D_s^{\\ast\n+} D_{s1}(2460)^- +c.c.$ are studied for the first time using data samples\ncollected with the BESIII detector at the BEPCII collider. The Born cross\nsections of $e^+e^-\\to D_s^+ D_{s1}(2460)^- +c.c.$ at nine center-of-mass\nenergies between 4.467\\,GeV and 4.600\\,GeV and those of $e^+e^-\\to D_s^{\\ast +}\nD_{s1}(2460)^- +c.c.$ at ${\\sqrt s}=$ 4.590\\,GeV and 4.600\\,GeV are measured.\nNo obvious charmonium or charmonium-like structure is seen in the measured\ncross sections.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 May 2020 15:12:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-25"}
